author: hwright
msg: Further remove an access baton which was just being used as a surrogate for the
adm_abspath.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/props.c
(svn_wc_merge_props3): Update caller.
(svn_wc__merge_props): Update params to use an adm_abspath and local_abspath
instead of an access baton and path.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/props.h
(svn_wc__merge_props): Update params and docs.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(close_directory, merge_props): Update callers.

author: rhuijben
msg: Make sure we always read svn_wc_conflict_version_t * as NULL when
deserializing an empty version instead of deserializing to an instance that
has invalid values. This makes the deserialized conflict match the
originally serialized conflict.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/tree_conflicts.c
(read_node_version_info): Update prototype. Return a NULL
svn_wc_conflict_version_t if it was written as a NULL
svn_wc_conflict_version_t.
